Package Model

Class Sale

java.lang.Object
Model.Sale
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Sale extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a sale of a pet. The sale has a pet, a discount, a sale date, and a price. The price of the pet is set to -1 when the pet is sold.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Group6
